Prayer

Heavenly Father, hallowed is your name

We are thankful for your gracious forgiveness of our sins and we pray for the courage to forgive those who have sinned against us

May the Holy Spirit cover this fellowship gathering. May He lead us in wisdom, guide our decisions and protect us from deception

Lord may you protect us from deception and evil

I ask that you make us disciples of your will to establish your kingdom here on earth as it is in heaven

May we have strong, enduring faith and trust your plan

In Jesus mighty name

Amen





